<body>
<div type="letter">
    
  <pb facs="1037819" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/><salute>Viro Illustrissimo atque Doctissimo <rs type="person">Sebastiano Checotio</rs>
    <lb/><rs type="person">N. B.</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
  <p><lb type="deleted"/><del>[...]</del>
    <lb/>Est quod te maximopere rogem, ut duo mihi condones; primum, cul<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>pam tam diu dilat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> responsionis, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> qua facienda <del>[...]</del>varia impedimen<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ta<del>[...]</del> cogitationes meas alio avertentia me
    <lb/>hucusque absterruerunt: alterum, fastidium quod fortassis tibi crea<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>bo, <del>[...]</del><add>si</add> dixero, me usque adeo difficilem et morosum esse, ut nec<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>dum per ultimam tuam <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> mihi satisfactum sit. Patere,
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, ut dicam, te semper assumere id, quod ego demonstratione
    <lb/>vel (si mavis) ulteriore explicatione opus habere affirmo. Asser<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem quidem tuam non nego, neque unquam negavi, sed modum
    <lb/>sive causam assertionis tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. Ais idem Curvilineum <formula>ABEC</formula> nostris 
    <pb facs="1037820" n="2"/> 
    <lb/>conditionibus satisfacturum, etiamsi significationes linearum <formula>AC</formula>, <formula>DC</formula>,
    <lb/><del>[...]</del><add>(</add>tempor<del>[...]</del><add>um</add>) et linearum <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>DE</formula> (virium) proportionaliter muten<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tur; <del>[...]</del>hoc quidem verum est, sed ratio hujus rei,
    <lb/><del>[...]</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te allata</add>, mihi videtur <add>esse</add> obscura, neque probe intelligo <del>[...]</del>id
    <lb/><del>[...]</del>qu<del>[...]</del><add>o</add>d<del>[...]</del> dicis, hoc ea de causa fieri, quoniam conditio<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nes Problematis nil pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter coordinatarum quarumlibet mutu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>am ad invicem relationem includant.<del>[...]</del>
    <lb/><del>[...]</del>Peto igitur ut ratiocinio Geometrico in
    <lb/>formam (si placet) syllogisticam redacto probes, omnes relationis termi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nos in qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stionem venientes, una cum quantitatibus illis, <del>[...]</del>quas <formula>G</formula>,
    <lb/><formula>T</formula>, <formula>S</formula>, appellabam, semper proportionaliter mutari, nullamque i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>u<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tabilem quantitatem ingredi in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quationem, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exprimit rela<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem coordinatarum Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <del>[...]</del><formula>BEC</formula>. Miror etiam quod
    <lb/>putes, in posteriore <rs type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> parte accuratissime demonstra<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ta esse, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cunque priori solution<del>[...]</del><add>i</add>s tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio">articulo</rs> proponuntur;
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so te, annon status qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stionis ille est, quem in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedente
    <lb/>mea <rs type="letter">epistola</rs> posui, <del>[...]</del>nempe an ex
    <lb/>assumta analogia <choice><orig><formula>AB.ab\;::\;AC.ac</formula></orig><reg><formula>AB:ab=AC:ac</formula></reg></choice> (vide <abbr>figg.</abbr> illius <rs type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>)
    <lb/>concludi debeat similitudo figurarum <formula>BECA</formula>, <formula>beca</formula>? jam tu
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stionem invertis, et ex assumta similitudine figurarum
    <lb/><formula>BECA</formula>, <formula>beca</formula>, aliquid (nescio quid, <del>[...]</del>nam circulum co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ittis
    <lb/>in illa demonstratione) demonstrare contendis. Ut omnis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qui<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>vocationis ansa pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cidatur, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stionem denuo sequenti mo<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>do formabo: Repr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentet recta linea <formula>T</formula> tempus aliquod determi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>natum, <add>et</add> recta <formula>V</formula> vim aliquam determinatam, cadat corpus in recta
    <lb/><formula>AaFfC</formula> ex diversis quietis punctis <formula>A</formula>, <formula>a</formula>, sitque curva <formula>CgGbB</formula>
    <lb/>curva virium, <formula>AED</formula> curva temporum pro descensu ex puncto <formula>A</formula>,
    <lb/><formula>aed</formula> curva temporum pro descensu ex puncto <formula>a</formula>; hoc est, repr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
    <pb facs="1037821" n="3"/><lb break="no"/>sen<del>[...]</del><add>t</add>entur <figure/> per rectas <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>ab</formula>, <formula>FG</formula>, <formula>fg</formula>,
    <lb/>quantitates absolut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> virium agen<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tium in punctis <formula>A</formula>, <formula>a</formula>, <formula>F</formula>, <formula>f</formula>; per re<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ctas <formula>DC</formula>, <formula>EF</formula>, <formula>dC</formula>, <formula>ef</formula>, quantitates ab<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>solut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> temporum per <formula>AC</formula>, <formula>AF</formula>, <formula>aC</formula>, <formula>af</formula>;
    <lb/>habeatque Curva virium <formula>CgGbB</formula> conditionem
    <lb/>Problematis nostri, id est, sit <choice><orig><formula>AB.ab\;::\;DC.dC</formula></orig><reg><formula>AB:ab=DC:dC</formula></reg></choice>. Dico debere
    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te ostendi, quod sumtis ordinatis <formula>FG</formula>, <formula>fg</formula> in ea ratione, ut sit
    <lb/><choice><orig><formula>AB.ab\;::\;FG.fg</formula></orig><reg><formula>AB:ab=FG:fg</formula></reg></choice>, sequatur ista analogia, <choice><orig><formula>DC.dC\;::\;EF.ef</formula></orig><reg><formula>DC:dC=EF:ef</formula></reg></choice>,
    <lb/>aut vice versa, quod sumendo <choice><orig><formula>DC.dC\;::\;EF.ef</formula></orig><reg><formula>DC:dC=EF:ef</formula></reg></choice> sequatur ista
    <lb/>analogia <choice><orig><formula>AB.ab\;::\;FG.fg</formula></orig><reg><formula>AB:ab=FG:fg</formula></reg></choice>; hic enim est sensus articuli primi <rs type="biblio">solutio<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nis</rs> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, cujus veram demonstratioem Geometricam etiamnum
    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te desidero.<del>[...]</del>
    <lb type="deleted"/><del>[...]</del>
    <lb/><del>[...]</del>Si aliquando te videndi occasionem haberem (de quo non despero)
    <lb/><del>[...]</del><add>n</add>on dubito quin litem hanc nostram subito confecturi esse<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>mus.<del>[...]</del>
  <lb type="deleted"/><del>[...]</del> </p>
  <lb/><closer><del>[...]</del><salute>Interim fac ut valeas et mihi
    <lb/>faveas. </salute><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Venetiis</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1719-06-16">16. Junii 1719</date>.</dateline></closer>
<postscript>
<p><lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Habito hic apud <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Petrum Antonium Michelotti</rs>.</p>
</postscript>
</div>
